comment._content: Could this perhaps be this team: en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BFC_Preussen#History The emblem on the shirts looks rather like the emblem shown on the page just mentioned. Or perhaps it's this one: en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Preussen_Munster which also shows a similar emblem. Finally, there's this club, which also has preussen in its name, though not a similar emblem: en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SV_Viktoria_Preußen_07
